$ON_NBCAR
Onevent BEFORE_INPUT Call AS_NBCAR From W1SITRACOD
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Call AV_NBCAR From W1SITRACOD
Return

Subprog AV_NBCAR
Local Decimal BASPAG
If adxgtb=1 & !GORITITCOL & nolign=1
 Local Char BASPAG(10)
 BASPAG = "NBCAR" : Gosub TIT_COL From W1SITRACOD
Endif
Gosub _AFF
End

Subprog AS_NBCAR
Local Decimal BASPAG
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(1002,GBOUT2) From OBJDIV
Onkey 130 Titled GBOUT2 Call B2_NBCAR From W1SITRACOD
Gosub _AFF
End

Subprog B2_NBCAR
Local Decimal BASPAG
If !GWEBSERV
 ## Action STD
 Call B2_NBCAR From SUBSITC
Endif
If mkstat=99 : mkstat = 0 : Elsif mkstat=0 : mkstat = 2 : Endif
Gosub _AFF
End

$ON_CAR1
Onevent BEFORE_INPUT Call AS_CAR1(zc) From W1SITRACOD
Onevent CONTROL Call C_CAR1(zc) From W1SITRACOD
Onevent AFTER_AREA Call AP_CAR1(zc) From W1SITRACOD
